01:36:30.740 --> 01:36:32.240
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:36:48.780 --> 01:36:51.530
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Maybe we ♪</font>

01:36:51.660 --> 01:36:54.200
<font color="#80ffff">♪ We don't have to be ♪</font>

01:36:57.910 --> 01:37:00.080
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Anonymous anymore. ♪</font>

01:37:05.700 --> 01:37:07.120
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:37:28.910 --> 01:37:31.700
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:37:36.000 --> 01:37:37.540
<font color="#ffff80">GIRL</font>: Can you imagine?

01:37:55.460 --> 01:37:57.250
Wh-What's wrong?

01:37:57.370 --> 01:37:59.000
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:38:02.910 --> 01:38:04.790
Yep.

01:38:17.920 --> 01:38:20.080
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:38:38.290 --> 01:38:39.580
Hi.

01:38:39.710 --> 01:38:41.370
{\an1}Alana, you have to
take it down, okay?

01:38:41.500 --> 01:38:43.040
They've been through enough.

01:38:43.170 --> 01:38:44.930
I took it down already,
Evan, but it-it doesn't matter

01:38:44.960 --> 01:38:46.210
because it's everywhere.

01:38:51.500 --> 01:38:54.250
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:38:54.380 --> 01:38:55.420
Zoe, it's me.

01:38:55.540 --> 01:38:56.670
Please call me back, okay?

01:38:56.790 --> 01:38:58.420
I'm worried about you.

01:38:58.540 --> 01:39:00.170
They have pictures of us now.

01:39:00.290 --> 01:39:01.580
Just put it away.

01:39:01.710 --> 01:39:03.590
"His parents act
like they are bereft,

01:39:03.710 --> 01:39:06.290
but where were they when
their son was actually alive?"

01:39:06.420 --> 01:39:08.460
Please stop reading them.

01:39:10.920 --> 01:39:13.130
- Hey. Is Zoe here?
- She went home.

01:39:15.290 --> 01:39:18.040
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:39:29.380 --> 01:39:30.620
Things really aren't good here.

01:39:30.670 --> 01:39:33.000
I know. I just... I had to come.

01:39:34.170 --> 01:39:36.100
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: Where did they even...
How did they get Connor's note?

01:39:36.130 --> 01:39:37.500
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: I don't know.

01:39:37.630 --> 01:39:39.310
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: Like, did
they hack our computers?

01:39:39.380 --> 01:39:41.060
They hacked our emails?
Did... These people are adults.

01:39:41.090 --> 01:39:42.550
Did you see their pictures?

01:39:42.670 --> 01:39:43.800
{\an1}These people are adults.

01:39:43.920 --> 01:39:45.420
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: Look, maybe let it ring.

01:39:45.550 --> 01:39:47.710
<font color="#ffff80">ZOE</font>: I'm sick of hiding. Hello?

01:39:47.840 --> 01:39:49.350
{\an1}Yeah, have-have fun
with your miserable life.

01:39:49.380 --> 01:39:51.100
LARRY</font>: What did they
say? What's the number?

01:39:51.170 --> 01:39:52.380
It's blocked.

01:39:52.500 --> 01:39:53.920
It doesn't... No,
it doesn't matter.

01:39:54.050 --> 01:39:55.730
CYNTHIA</font>: That's it.
I'm calling the police.

01:39:55.800 --> 01:39:56.810
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: No, look, right now,
maybe the best thing to do

01:39:56.840 --> 01:39:58.590
is to just stay calm, all right?

01:39:58.710 --> 01:39:59.050
And sit...

01:39:59.060 --> 01:40:00.480
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: That's always
your solution, isn't it?

01:40:00.500 --> 01:40:01.900
Wait and see. Let's just
wait and see, right, Larry?

01:40:01.920 --> 01:40:03.060
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: What are
the police going to do?

01:40:03.090 --> 01:40:04.300
It's the Internet. Wh...

01:40:04.420 --> 01:40:05.920
Are they gonna
arrest the Internet?

01:40:06.050 --> 01:40:07.150
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: I had to beg
you, every step of the way,

01:40:07.170 --> 01:40:08.270
for-for therapy, for-for rehab.

01:40:08.300 --> 01:40:09.920
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: What? N-No, no.

01:40:10.050 --> 01:40:11.820
You went lurching from
one miracle cure to the next...

01:40:11.840 --> 01:40:13.420
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: Oh, you're... Really?

01:40:13.550 --> 01:40:15.480
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: ...because all he
needed was another $20,000

01:40:15.510 --> 01:40:16.510
weekend yoga retreat.

01:40:16.590 --> 01:40:17.960
What was your alternative,

01:40:18.090 --> 01:40:19.520
{\an1}other than picking apart
everything that I did?

01:40:19.550 --> 01:40:21.460
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: How about putting him on

01:40:21.590 --> 01:40:23.210
one program and sticking to it?

01:40:23.340 --> 01:40:25.130
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: Remember what he said

01:40:25.260 --> 01:40:27.220
the first time that Connor
tried to kill himself?

01:40:27.340 --> 01:40:28.900
- That he's just looking for attention.
- For Christ's sake.

01:40:28.920 --> 01:40:30.420
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: He just
wants attention!

01:40:30.550 --> 01:40:32.230
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: I'm not gonna
sit here and defend myself!

01:40:32.260 --> 01:40:33.690
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: You
couldn't understand him.

01:40:33.720 --> 01:40:36.670
{\an1}You never understood him
because he wasn't yours!

01:40:36.800 --> 01:40:38.840
Mom, what the hell?

01:40:38.970 --> 01:40:40.780
I raised him from the time
he was three years old.

01:40:40.800 --> 01:40:42.400
He was getting better, and
you refused to see it. Ask Evan.

01:40:42.420 --> 01:40:44.260
Tell them, Evan.

01:40:44.380 --> 01:40:46.050
Evan did everything
that he could.

01:40:46.170 --> 01:40:48.970
{\an1}Evan? Evan was in denial
of what was happening.

01:40:49.090 --> 01:40:50.760
<font color="#ffff80">ZOE</font>: Do not bring him into this.

01:40:50.880 --> 01:40:52.060
<font color="#ffff80">CYNTHIA</font>: Read the note, Larry.

01:40:52.090 --> 01:40:53.590
Read what he said.

01:40:53.720 --> 01:40:55.630
<i>"I just wish that
everything was different."</i>

01:40:55.760 --> 01:40:57.550
LARRY</font>: <i>I tried.</i>

01:40:57.680 --> 01:40:59.190
- But he was my son!
- <font color="#ffff80">He wanted to be better! - ZOE</font>: Please.

01:40:59.220 --> 01:41:00.340
<font color="#ffff80">LARRY</font>: I-I tried everything!

01:41:00.470 --> 01:41:02.010
<font color="#ffff80">ZOE</font>: Stop it! Just please stop!

01:41:02.130 --> 01:41:04.430
- Please stop fighting!
- He was trying to be better!

01:41:04.550 --> 01:41:05.430
He was trying!

01:41:05.550 --> 01:41:07.010
And he was failing.

01:41:07.130 --> 01:41:09.260
We failed him.

01:41:10.300 --> 01:41:11.720
No, you didn't. No, you didn't.

01:41:11.840 --> 01:41:12.970
You didn't fail him.

01:41:15.180 --> 01:41:16.430
Read the note.

01:41:18.300 --> 01:41:19.970
He didn't write it.

01:41:25.760 --> 01:41:27.050
I wrote it.

01:41:27.180 --> 01:41:30.550
You didn't write
Connor's suicide note.

01:41:31.510 --> 01:41:35.260
{\an1}Um, it was an assignment
from my therapist.

01:41:35.390 --> 01:41:37.300
Write a letter to
yourself, um, a pep talk.

01:41:37.430 --> 01:41:39.450
"Evan Hansen, Dear Evan
Hansen, today's gonna be a good day.

01:41:39.470 --> 01:41:41.150
{\an1}- Here's why."
- I-I don't, I don't think that...

01:41:41.180 --> 01:41:42.950
I was supposed to bring it
to my appointment with me,

01:41:42.970 --> 01:41:45.150
but Connor took it, and then
I guess he must have had it

01:41:45.180 --> 01:41:47.050
with him, um...

01:41:49.220 --> 01:41:51.600
...when you found him, so...

01:41:56.390 --> 01:41:57.850
What are you saying?

01:41:59.600 --> 01:42:01.140
We weren't friends.

01:42:01.260 --> 01:42:02.640
No.

01:42:02.760 --> 01:42:04.140
No, no, no, no.

01:42:04.260 --> 01:42:06.600
<font color="#80ffff">♪ I never meant to
make it such a mess ♪</font>

01:42:08.640 --> 01:42:11.390
<font color="#80ffff">♪ I never thought that
it would go this far ♪</font>

01:42:11.510 --> 01:42:13.890
{\an1}There were emails.
You showed us emails.

01:42:14.010 --> 01:42:18.180
<font color="#80ffff">♪ So I just stand here sorry ♪</font>

01:42:18.310 --> 01:42:20.810
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Searching for
something to say ♪</font>

01:42:20.930 --> 01:42:22.010
Mm.

01:42:22.140 --> 01:42:23.510
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Something to say ♪</font>

01:42:23.640 --> 01:42:25.930
Y-Y-You knew about the orchard.

01:42:26.060 --> 01:42:28.180
He-he took you to the orchard.

01:42:28.310 --> 01:42:29.970
That's where you broke your arm.

01:42:30.100 --> 01:42:33.640
I broke my arm in Ellison
Park, um, by myself.

01:42:33.760 --> 01:42:36.140
But that day at the orchard...

01:42:37.890 --> 01:42:39.810
You and Connor at the orchard.

01:42:39.930 --> 01:42:41.970
<font color="#80ffff">♪ ♪</font>

01:42:44.100 --> 01:42:46.140
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Words fail ♪</font>

01:42:47.220 --> 01:42:49.270
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Words fail ♪</font>

01:42:50.720 --> 01:42:53.390
<font color="#80ffff">♪ There's nothing I can say ♪</font>

01:42:53.520 --> 01:42:54.970
Oh, God.

01:42:56.930 --> 01:42:59.350
But you said that you
guys would talk about me.

01:42:59.470 --> 01:43:01.350
He would...

01:43:01.470 --> 01:43:02.930
How could you do this?

01:43:03.060 --> 01:43:05.600
{\an1}<font color="#80ffff">♪ I guess I thought I
could be part of this ♪</font>

01:43:07.020 --> 01:43:09.930
<font color="#80ffff">♪ I never had this
kind of thing before ♪</font>

01:43:11.350 --> 01:43:14.430
<font color="#80ffff">♪ I never had
that perfect girl ♪</font>

01:43:14.560 --> 01:43:19.680
{\an1}<font color="#80ffff">♪ Who somehow could
see the good part of me ♪</font>

01:43:21.180 --> 01:43:23.640
{\an1}<font color="#80ffff">♪ I never had the
dad who stuck it out ♪</font>

01:43:25.140 --> 01:43:28.930
<font color="#80ffff">♪ No corny jokes
or baseball gloves ♪</font>

01:43:29.060 --> 01:43:31.430
<font color="#80ffff">♪ No mom who just was there ♪</font>

01:43:31.560 --> 01:43:36.940
{\an1}<font color="#80ffff">♪ 'Cause mom was
all that she had to be ♪</font>

01:43:37.060 --> 01:43:40.940
<font color="#80ffff">♪ That's not a
worthy explanation ♪</font>

01:43:41.060 --> 01:43:43.890
<font color="#80ffff">♪ I know there is none ♪</font>

01:43:45.940 --> 01:43:51.440
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Nothing can make sense
of all these things I've done ♪</font>

01:43:53.390 --> 01:43:58.100
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Words fail, words fail ♪</font>

01:43:58.230 --> 01:44:01.690
<font color="#80ffff">♪ There's nothing I can say ♪</font>

01:44:01.810 --> 01:44:05.270
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Except sometimes you
see everything you wanted ♪</font>

01:44:05.390 --> 01:44:07.480
<font color="#80ffff">♪ And sometimes ♪</font>

01:44:07.600 --> 01:44:09.940
<font color="#80ffff">♪ You see everything
you wish you had ♪</font>

01:44:10.060 --> 01:44:15.020
<font color="#80ffff">♪ And it's right there,
right there, right there ♪</font>

01:44:15.150 --> 01:44:17.350
<font color="#80ffff">♪ In front of you ♪</font>

01:44:22.230 --> 01:44:25.360
<font color="#80ffff">♪ And you want
to believe it's true ♪</font>

01:44:31.400 --> 01:44:34.360
<font color="#80ffff">♪ So you make it true ♪</font>

01:44:38.060 --> 01:44:41.730
<font color="#80ffff">♪ And you think maybe ♪</font>

01:44:41.860 --> 01:44:47.310
<font color="#80ffff">♪ Everybody wants it ♪</font>

01:44:49.980 --> 01:44:51.650
<font color="#80ffff">♪ And needs it ♪</font>

01:44:53.560 --> 01:44:57.070
<font color="#80ffff">♪ A little bit, too. ♪</font>

01:45:13.650 --> 01:45:14.900
LARRY</font>: Zoe.

